<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>L'Impact Forfeo | Ambassadeurs d'Élite</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .hover-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .hover-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .stat-value { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; color: #007bff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white shadow-sm sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary" href="/">FORFEO LAB</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler border-0" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navAmb">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navAmb">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Accueil</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/login">Connexion</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <h1 class="text-center fw-bold mb-5">Pourquoi devenir Ambassadeur ?</h1>
        
        <div class="row g-4 text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="hover-card shadow-sm border">
                    <div class="stat-value">+25%</div>
                    <p class="fw-bold fs-5">Croissance CA</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Impact moyen sur le chiffre d'affaires des entreprises partenaires.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="hover-card shadow-sm border">
                    <div class="stat-value">4.9/5</div>
                    <p class="fw-bold fs-5">E-Réputation</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Note moyenne obtenue par nos clients après 3 mois d'audits.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="hover-card shadow-sm border">
                    <div class="stat-value">91%</div>
                    <p class="fw-bold fs-5">Fidélisation</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted">Des clients qui reviennent grâce à un service corrigé et parfait.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <a href="/ambassadeur/inscription" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 fw-bold">REJOINDRE LE CERCLE</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
